            <title>[SPR-9897] YamlPropertiesFactoryBean and YamlMapFactoryBean</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-9897</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Yaml is a nice human friendly way to specify maps and configuration externalizations (e.g. as an alternative to properties files).  the easiest way to consume it in Java would be as a Map&amp;lt;String,Object&amp;gt; (like a JSON object) or as Properties.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
